'''The Atomic Punk''' was a closed-down nightclub on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Yukka]], in the heart of the capital city's dust belt. It was used as a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] base during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. In this incarnation, bunks and equipment were all over the floor, and the D.J.'s booth was used as a monitoring station, where an [[Engineer/Legends|engineer]] would always monitor the system traffic using a large [[Sensor array/Legends|sensor array]] that the Rebels had acquired.

A group of Rebels came to the base after [[Alliance Intelligence/Legends|Rebel Intelligence]] learned of the [[D-Wing Space Superiority Fighter|D-wing]], which was being shown at the [[Cynestra Space Craft Show]]. They met up with [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Reeves]], who gave them all the information necessary for them to capture the D-wing prototype.

